    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.283165>
    bibo:endPage "62" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "51" ;
    bibo:volume "3590" ;
    dc:creator "Kononenko, Vladimir S.; Volynkin, Anton V.; Yu, Alexei" ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "A revision of the Xestia (Radddea) alexis (Kozhanchikov, 1928) species-group with a checklist of subgenus Raddea Alphéraky, 1892 and description of brachipterous females (Lepidoptera, Noctuidae, Noctuinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.283167> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.283167>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7 – 32. 7. Xestia alexis, female, Altai (right—dorsal view, left—lateral view); 8. X. herrichschaefferi, female, Altai (right—dorsal view, left—lateral view); 9 – 16. Series of males of X. alexis, showing variability of the species; 17 – 24. Series of males of X. herrichschaefferi, showing variability of the species; 25 – 32. Northern species of the genus Xestia, subgenus Pachnobia with brachypterous females. 25, 26 — X. aequava, 27, 28 — X. alaskae; 29, 30 — X. liquidaria; 31, 32 — X. kurentzovi (right male, left female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/283167/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

